      "role": "user",
      "content": "friend or professional? what’s the point. they don't get it. they see me and they just see a person who lost a relationship, but it’s like my whole foundation is just gone. i look at the future and it’s just... empty. it's not even sadness anymore, it's just this massive, hollow nothingness. how am i supposed to just keep going through the motions every single day when there is literally nothing waiting for me?",
